1. Fork this project (you can use GitHub, https://github.com/jonathancast/logophile).
2. Make improvements, fix bugs, add docs, etc.
3. Update the COPYRIGHT and CONTRIBUTORS files to include yourself and license your changes under the PSL.
4. Push the changes to your fork.
5. Email me at jonathanccast@fastmail.fm.
6. I'll mention your fork as an alternative version of Logophile on the logophile-desktop.com website.
7. If I like your changes, I'll pull from your fork. I might also have suggestions for you if I feel like it!
8. If you bug me about responding to you, I'll set up an email filter to throw away your emails.
